Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:02.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The land of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:06.08,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time, long ago, when our country was called by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:11.26,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,With the arrival of the Amanto from outer space and the Sword Ban twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.71,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,the samurai class fell into decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:20.30,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,In these hard times, there was one man left with the spirit of the samurai. His name is Gintoki Sakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:25.38,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura and I, Shinpachi Shimura, work at Odd Jobs Gin, which is coincidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.52,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:31.18,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you reuse the introduction now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:33.18,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is supposed to be a new show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.79,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We have to explain the context for the newcomers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:39.85,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time to worry about the context of this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.98,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The audience is only kind of paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:44.75,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:50.67,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So Gintama is kind of back in 16:9.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.18,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The first episode of Gintama in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.48,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a little time to get back in the flow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.33,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but for now, it's back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:41.47,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Odd Jobs Gin-chan]\N[Snack Otose]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.47,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I haven't been here in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:40.76,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.90,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, we're finally back on air...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.99,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.31,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Vacation's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.61,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The show is back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.77,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This town hasn't changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.23,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's walking around with glum faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:03.00,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.07,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.59,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:06.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:07.27,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.24,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:13.60,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't find anything to do while we ran reruns for a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.11,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.08,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.35,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.12,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You even forgot my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:27.18,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say it only takes a man three days to grow out of his boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.06,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:31.96,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:37.82,Default,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Everyone Looks a Little Grown Up After Spring Break]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.72,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.17,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Pachi-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.49,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.10,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.11,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's been a year since the show was last on air...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:49.67,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell happened to you in the past year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:52.27,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's long enough for my hair to grow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:55.34,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Forget your hair!  You look like a completely different character!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:59.37,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting like we just ran into each other for the first time in years at the World Martial Arts Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.74,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have a scar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.69,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that patch on your chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.11,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.00,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget the promise we made?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:06.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.47,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,After the show ended, we held a little pow wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.33,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:11.16,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.68,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.43,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,With the TV show and movie over with,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:17.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gintama was starting to lose its novelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.31,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So we discussed how it was necessary to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:23.13,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,give the show a breath of fresh air to keep the fans interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:28.05,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Each of us would use this break to work on a remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.73,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And then we would return to New Odd Jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.58,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet up at Jabaody Archipelago in two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:37.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We never made any promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is Jabaody Archipelago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.32,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.39,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It comes down to feeling and inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:44.76,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Inspiration, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.29,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You stole that promise from a different anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.21,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was waiting for you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:51.15,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I spent all my time training hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.64,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.41,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I had a rough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.92,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Getting blown up by weird aliens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.10,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Impaled by cyborgs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.89,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Losing my woman to some guy with a mad widow's peak...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.74,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You keep using flashbacks from other shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.51,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And you did all of this in one year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.19,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? One year?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.57,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.67,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Two years have passed in this anime in the past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.33,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not much of a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.56,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And you're clearly lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.71,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this show follows the Sazae format where nobody ages...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.86,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.86,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at how much I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.05,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.25,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.97,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.21,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,How you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.25,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.59,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Did you shrink, Shinpachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.80,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:36.74,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.80,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.37,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.39,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:48.06,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You look exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.06,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.26,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This guy didn't do anything the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.43,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:53.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-cha-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.99,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:58.31,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:01.53,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,They say it only takes a woman three days to grow out of her boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No, they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.26,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired after the long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.30,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.28,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's something else we need to address first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.38,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow, Nappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.51,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:15.50,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She changed into her pajamas and plopped herself on the couch the moment she got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.83,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She's grown into one hell of a pajama girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.98,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Am I supposed to be impressed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.21,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And what was the point in standing on my head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.77,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura, where were you training?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.47,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.71,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I flew around space with Pappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.72,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I brought some souvenirs you can eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:30.70,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.36,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.78,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I already ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.98,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.24,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,He finished them off before I even mentioned them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.79,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan's grown into one hell of a greedy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.97,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be considered growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:45.01,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And do you feel you have to stand on my head to look impressive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:49.52,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that my two years of training wasn't for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:52.41,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start a new legend here at New Odd Jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.55,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.89,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.78,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, the two of you have regressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.00,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, is it true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.31,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Two years have passed while I wasn't paying attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.92,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody told me about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I the only one left behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.89,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when you treat the break as a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:13.03,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to work hard when people aren't watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:17.59,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's trying to convince everyone you were training during the break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:30.51,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Sugar Content]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:22.82,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I want to know how you're able to look exactly the same after two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.27,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Two years is enough for ramen to grow stale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:29.03,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Sadaharu tagged along with me and grew a lot, Nappa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.51,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop calling me Nappa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.91,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it must be Sadaharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:38.22,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Pets weren't allowed on my ship, so I had to put him on a different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.50,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.28,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say that he grew a lot, Kagura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.82,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, he looks smaller now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.23,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:56.45,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Odd Jobs Gin-chan]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.38,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.06,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:07.97,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, our pet just ran off, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.75,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:14.62,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,I, Sadaharu, have finished serving my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.97,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.29,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.24,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly the delivery man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That dog was obviously Sadaharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.35,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,That was a delivery dog from Planet Komainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:30.25,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu's shy, so I had him delivered by a dog just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.19,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Just like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That was obviously Sadaharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:35.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And they don't look anything like each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.41,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, he grew a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.29,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't called growing a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.33,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is called turning into a completely different creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:46.63,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi, dogs grow faster than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.01,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Two years is enough for them to become old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.86,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is literally just an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.93,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Shinpachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.56,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,if I've done anything to offend you, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.47,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:00.55,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't blame Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.64,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,I will make amends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.10,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,If a doggy or two will satisfy you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.02,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.39,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.80,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by doggy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.40,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this remind me of pinky amputation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.58,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this Sadaharu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he acting like a direct-to-video fan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:16.96,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:17.88,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.71,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,On closer look, there's something at the end of his tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.77,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.19,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's a small Sadaharu on his tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:23.51,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.33,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.24,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.65,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I tell you an old story?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:37.05,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,There was a very happy dog who belonged to very wonderful owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:44.55,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,However, the dog always wondered if he was worthy of his owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:49.00,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,In order to join his owners as they marched on, to move forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.43,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,the dog chose to fight alongside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:56.17,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day, he would place his tail in scorching sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.52,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:01.73,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day, he would make his tail watch Karate Kid 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.85,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:08.13,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, a firm wart appeared on his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.66,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,It continued to grow bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.22,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,However, as the wart grew in size,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.87,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,his body shrunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.67,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,As though the wart was sapping his strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.92,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:22.00,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right - I am that wart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.33,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How could I possibly understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.60,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, the wart traded places with the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.60,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's so short that I have no idea what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.20,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.46,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu and I may be different in appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.82,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,but our minds are connected through this tail, and we share the same destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.09,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,You can call us the Wartio Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.48,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.13,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Wartiharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.63,Default,Sadaharu,0000,0000,0000,,It is an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.61,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna call you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:45.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to keep this freak as a pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.07,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:47.85,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.93,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Nappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.22,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.54,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.51,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san and Kagura are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.48,Default,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.95,Default,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just barge into a lady's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.80,Default,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,You should knock first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.68,Default,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a fight going on, Master Shinpachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:07.12,Default,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably something stupid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.44,Default,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.20,Default,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time to listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.72,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.74,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.95,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They were lying about two years passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:18.52,Default,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.51,Default,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.33,Default,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,...quite some time since I've seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.62,Default,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,A long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.58,Default,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,A very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.15,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're all Wartiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.22,Default,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you recognize us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.07,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to recognize!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.93,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've all evolved into different creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.99,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And an android is capable of growing warts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:39.60,Default,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,They were all intent on improving themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:42.74,Default,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,and after pushing themselves too hard for two years, we were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:46.33,Default,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,For now, you can call us Wartise, Wartirine, and Warti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.80,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So there's nothing left of Tama-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.56,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:54.51,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,everybody's been working hard while you weren't watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.31,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We've all been trying to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.82,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Only their warts have grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.54,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Pachi-boy, it doesn't matter what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.09,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The past two years aren't coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.58,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You have to face reality and look to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have plenty of chances to redeem yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.73,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you're denying yourself that chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.53,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to create a wart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.36,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You bet I'm gonna deny that chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.83,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.43,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There was a two year jump during the one year break like in One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.49,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Warts turning into old men...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.50,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody leaving me behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.27,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to accept this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.24,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, may I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.09,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.57,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.68,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like everyone's gone to a faraway place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.94,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I've experienced this many times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.98,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I dream about this all the time, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:08.76,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We're all running in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.04,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone else is faster than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.09,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I try my best to catch up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.58,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but I end up alone in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.99,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, you're a lucky boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:28.29,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Because you have a goal to guide you through the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:33.73,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The truly unfortunate are those who stand still without any sense of which direction to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:40.97,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,And it's hardest on the person who's running out in front when he can't tell left from right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:46.65,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,True, they aren't nice enough to slow down for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.82,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,They may take a lot of detours...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:54.79,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,But you believe that he's moving forward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.19,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,You're very fortunate to have someone like that, Shin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.84,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far away he gets, you'll still be able to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.71,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,And as long as you keep moving, I know that you'll be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.16,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,It only makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:12.75,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'll be there to kick you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.11,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.14,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.63,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.99,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if two years have passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:26.00,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I can go anywhere if I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.45,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,That's the little brother I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.69,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,You can hang on tight to the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.67,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.39,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,But I promise to take you to Neverland!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:37.15,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:40.97,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so excited that you forget about us, Isao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.93,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'll always be right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.33,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're all happy, let's have dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.29,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, or you won't get any!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:50.32,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait for me, Isao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.76,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,What's for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.98,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.19,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,What? Curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.09,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Omelets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.05,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.66,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.76,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,This will help me forget everything bad that's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.66,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Isao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.95,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Open wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.01,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Otae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.40,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I can eat my own food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.30,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please, why are you acting so shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.25,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We're married now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.58,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,This is a perfectly normal thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:31.84,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.86,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would be able to guess which one of us used to stalk the other one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.92,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:39.79,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known how kind you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:42.12,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I could have found happiness much sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:46.29,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that you would quit the Shinsengumi and help us with our dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.75,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinsengumi can do fine without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.94,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,They have plenty of responsible people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.33,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,But it's my job to support you, Otae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.22,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hopeless without you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.06,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.25,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.57,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:05.68,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.87,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,You barely touched your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:09.28,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,You need to eat so you can work, Shinpachi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.20,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.95,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Today's your first day on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.10,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:17.62,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Isao-san helped you find this wonderful job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.82,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,so you need to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:19.93,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:25.81,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good to know that you'll be there to replace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.22,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trusting you to take care of the Shinsengumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.44,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We won't see each other much since you'll be living there while training,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.65,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,but do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.77,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:38.11,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,No, the three of us will always be here to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.16,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.15,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.03,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.77,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Three of us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.35,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, you'll be an uncle when you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:51.65,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Become a samurai that will make this child proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:55.10,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really, Otae-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.84,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.03,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Shinpachi-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:58.89,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.10,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.73,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,He's fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:05.56,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he's a very dependable little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.38,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,No, a very dependable uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:09.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was when Ikazo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.66,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you shitting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.09,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.97,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done to deserve this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:32.10,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I go on vacation for a year and this is what happens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.30,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.77,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The Odd Jobs members have changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:37.14,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And what's worse, that gorilla of a stalker somehow managed to land my sister
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:40.19,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and become my older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.09,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the third wheel now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.31,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They sent me to the Shinsengumi to get me out of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.61,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely out of the loop at Odd Jobs, at my own home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:53.01,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This short amount of time was all it took to leave me with nowhere to belong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.37,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.76,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm the only person left in an unknown world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.56,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.09,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.14,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I was once in your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.12,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ky-Kyubei-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.78,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She totally looks like a girl now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.83,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And her hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.54,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:24.68,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.03,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with touching men now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.85,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:30.99,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.24,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ignore you when I saw you crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.44,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Otae-chan is gone now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.91,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided that I needed to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.26,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Because she lost my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.28,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I look strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.30,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sorry about what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.52,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You look really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.93,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.49,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:58.40,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Shinpachi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.62,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,you aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.04,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.04,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,So you can come here when you're feeling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.70,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I come here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.67,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,It helps when there's someone else who feels the same way as you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:13.11,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,And do you mind if I ask a favor in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:14.12,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.84,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:19.30,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Could you experiment by touching me from time to time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.14,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.34,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.38,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that I'm fine when you touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.18,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.35,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because you resemble Tae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.45,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.59,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,M-My heart is about to burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:36.46,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I want to forget about Tae-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.12,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I have to learn to live with men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:42.67,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.34,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:46.86,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Was Kyubei-san always this cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.10,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.10,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.18,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I can help you every day if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you with anything you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.47,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I can touch you every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.66,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.16,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.71,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Then touch me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.67,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Please be gentle when you experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.21,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.01,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:08.56,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.58,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If I experiment there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.33,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.93,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.67,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...turn into a mad scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:24.73,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.91,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's something here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.94,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Something that feels very familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.26,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.83,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,How is it compared to yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.99,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I just finished having the procedure,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:37.16,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't tell, is there anything abnormal about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:39.74,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What procedure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:40.84,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,For that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.13,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.01,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,The procedure to attach a male organ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.31,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:52.55,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You were asking me to touch your balls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:55.80,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike before, I'm a woman on the outside and a man on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.00,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I've been completely reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.53,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've only made it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.44,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of trying to become a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:08.19,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I search for a new world where gender doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.22,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,with those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kyu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, it's the cutie from Odd Jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She's aiming for a incredibly wrong new world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.92,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyu-chan's trying to steal him! Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.92,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's bon voyage to a new world with the blue beard pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:21.43,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you working at a gay bar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:24.34,Default,Kyube,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, I'm their ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.48,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so proud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:28.31,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is so crazy that I have no idea what's going on anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.87,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Sir Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.42,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You actually attached that foul member to your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:36.11,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you're intent on making your character overlap with mine.
