Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.09,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,We only differ in gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.47,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to eliminate that difference and take over my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:47.23,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,But I was one step ahead of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.75,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,While you were attaching that foul member...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:51.53,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:58.67,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Became Zurako!
